            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLaethd20">Oxford, Bodleian Library, Bodleian Aeth. d. 20</ref>,
                    without subscription and supplications.</note>

                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab>ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ብዙኅ፡ አልህምት፡ ወመፍቀሬ፡ ምጽዋት፡ ውእቱ። ወይሴፎ፡ ምጽአተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወመድኃኒቶሙ፡ ለእስራኤል፡ ወመጽኡ፡ ፈያት፡ እምሰብአ፡ ሀገረ፡ ቍድስ፡ ላዕላይ፡ ወሠረቁ፡ እምነ፡ አልህምቲሁ፡ ብዙኃ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ጥጥምና፤ ወየኃድር፡ ጎረቤቱ፡ ኀበ፡ ሀሎ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab>ወይቤሎሙ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ኀደጉ፡ ለክሙ፡ ኃጣዊክሙ፡ ለእመ፡ አመንክሙ፡ ብየ። ወሶቤሃ፡ አምኑ፡ ቦቱ። ወርእዩ፡ ስብሐተ፡ መንክራቲሁ። ጥጥምናሂ፡ አግብአ፡ አልህምቲሁ፡ እንዘ፡ ይትፌሣሕ። ወጸንዓ፡ ሃይማኖቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወአተወ፡ ቤቶ፡ እንዘ፡ የአኵት፡ ወይሴብሕ።</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="edition">
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BGRGT37I"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1917</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note><citedRange unit="page">643</citedRange></bibl>
                  <ab>
                    ወሀሎ፡ በህየ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ አልህምት፡ ብዙኅ፨ ወመፍቀሬ፡ ምጽዋት፡ ውእቱ። ወይሴፎ፡ ምጽአተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ መድኃኒቶሙ፡ ለእስራኤል። ወመጽኡ፡ ፈያት፡ እምሰብአ፡ ሀገረ፡ ቍድስ፡ ላዕላይ፡ ወሠረቁ፡ እምነ፡ አልህምቲሁ፡ ብዙኅ። ወስሙ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ጥጥምና።
                  </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BGRGT37I"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1917</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note><citedRange unit="page">645</citedRange></bibl>
                  <ab>
                    ወጥጥምናሂ፡ አግብአ፡ አልህምቲሁ፡ እንዘ፡ ይትፌሣሕ፨ ወጸንዐ፡ ሃይማኖቱ፡ በእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ወአተወ፡ ቤቶ፡ እንዘ፡ ይሴብሕ፡ ወያአኵት።
                  </ab>
